Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Taguilid Barangay High School Located in the Municipality of Pamplona, Province of Camarines Sur, into Don Mariano Veneracion Community High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 848
An Act Changing the Name of the Taguilid Barangay High School Located in the Municipality of Pamplona, Province of Camarines Sur, into Don Mariano Veneracion Community High School
Section 1. The barangay high school located at Barangay Veneracion in the Municipality of Pamplona Province of Camarines Sur, now known as the Taguilid Barangay High School hereafter be known as Don Mariano Veneracion Community High School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
